imdb.plot outline: Carolina and Chris are newlyweds from New York City who moved south to capitalize on the dynamic Florida real estate market. Flipping Miami follows this dynamic couple as husband Chris handles all property deals while his sexy wife Carolina wears the tool belt and runs the construction sites. Originally from Long Island, tough-talking Chris is a keen negotiator, but he admits he's nothing compared to his Colombian wife who won't hesitate to swing a hammer herself if she can't get the deal she wants from her contractors. Of course, when the sun sets, the two get to relax and enjoy the glamorous Miami night life where the beachside clubs are as hot and steamy as the hurricane season weather.
